pageContext.claim: “We have the best job numbers in the history of our country -- African American, Asian American, women, Hispanic American -- best job numbers we've ever had.”
pageContext.analysis: The unemployment rate under Trump is not the lowest in history. Neither is the African American unemployment rate, or the rate for women. The Asian American jobless rate has been reported for less than 20 years, so it's a stretch to claim a historical record there, too.
